OL,5,Cmoped
OL,7,FA teenager has been found guilty of
OL,8,Ffatally stabbing a 16-year-old boy
OL,9,Fwith a 30cm machete in a row over a
OL,10,Fstolen moped.
OL,12,FThe victim, Kamari Johnson, was found
OL,13,Finjured after police were called to
OL,14,FBourne Avenue in Hayes, west London,
OL,15,Fat about 1.30pm on 24 May 2024, and
OL,16,Fdied at the scene.
OL,18,FOn Tuesday, a 17-year-old youth was
OL,19,Ffound guilty at the Old Bailey of
OL,20,FKamari's murder and having an article
OL,21,Fwith a blade or point.
