OL,4,Cstabbing 16-year-old boy over stolen
OL,5,Cmoped
OL,7,FThe court had previously heard how the
OL,8,Fboys had been in contact over Snapchat
OL,9,Fabout the defendant's desire to buy a
OL,10,Fmoped from Kamari.
OL,12,FProsecutor Joel Smith KC had said the
OL,13,Ftwo "haggled" over a price with Kamari
OL,14,Fwanting #180 for it.
OL,16,FWhen they met to complete the sale,
OL,17,FKamari reneged on their agreement,
OL,18,Ftook the defendant's cash and drove
OL,19,Faway, the court heard.
