OL,7,FMinutes after the meeting, the 17-year-
OL,8,Fold, who cannot be identified for
OL,9,Flegal reasons, walked to Kamari's
OL,10,Fhouse to confront him, intent on
OL,11,Fgetting the bike, the court heard.
OL,13,FMr Smith said: "He knew where Mr
OL,14,FJohnson lived and he went there
OL,15,Flooking for him, and when he found
OL,16,Fhim, he stabbed him.
