OL,7,F"He stabbed him once through his chest
OL,8,Fand into his heart, and although Mr
OL,9,FJohnson managed to flee on the moped,
OL,10,Fhe collapsed minutes later and died on
OL,11,Fthe street."
OL,13,FThe jury was shown CCTV footage in
OL,14,Fwhich the defendant could be seen
OL,15,Fturning into the victim's road.
OL,17,FAbout 20 seconds later, the victim was
OL,18,Fshown driving out of the road on a
OL,19,Fblack moped while the defendant
OL,20,Ffollowed on foot, carrying a large
OL,21,Fknife with a curved blade.
