OL,7,FA witness, who can be seen in the
OL,8,Fclip, described seeing the defendant
OL,9,Fcarrying a blood-stained knife he
OL,10,Festimated to be about 30cm long, the
OL,11,Fprosecutor said.
OL,13,FAnother video played in court showed
OL,14,FKamari crashing the moped in a nearby
OL,15,Fpub car park and then collapsing.
OL,17,FIn police interviews, the defendant
OL,18,Fdeclined to answer questions but
OL,19,Fclaimed in a prepared statement that
OL,20,Fhe "acted in self-defence at all
OL,21,Ftimes".
