OL,7,FThe youth made no reaction and
OL,8,FKamari's family members wept in court
OL,9,Fas the verdicts were given after a
OL,10,Fjury deliberated for 13 hours and 35
OL,11,Fminutes.
OL,13,FJudge Simon Mayo KC thanked jurors for
OL,14,Ftheir service and adjourned sentencing
OL,15,Funtil 2pm on March 14.
OL,17,FThe judge also paid tribute to
OL,18,FKamari's family who remained "composed
OL,19,Fand acted in a very dignified fashion
OL,20,Fthroughout this trial".
